Adapter to provide Betfair SOAP API users ability to use Smarkets API

Dependencies:
	- ZSI
		http://sourceforge.net/projects/pywebsvcs/files/latest/download?source=files
		sudo python setup.py build install
	- smk_python_sdk
		https://github.com/smarkets/smk_python_sdk
		sudo python setup.py build install


Running:
	- set next environment variables:
		TEST_SMK_LOGIN    - mandatory
		TEST_SMK_PASSWORD - mandatory
		SMK_API_HOST      - defaults to smarkets API sandbox host
		SMK_API_PORT      - defaults to smarkets API sandbox port
		BETFAIR_API_PORT  - defaults to 8080
	- run "make test" to ensure everything works fine
	- run "make start" to start the adapter
	- run "make stop" to stop the adapter